	phase 2: create game loop and add inputs to it
		thread that refress screen every 60 frames per second
		add the inputs in this class

	phase 3: add gameobject
		create a class gameobject with life,direction and every things that a game character might have
		extend that class to create player 
		later do same for npc and enemy

	phase 4: add background 
		create a background class that contains image or background
		
	phase 5: add collision detection form youtube video

	phase 6: run the game
		this should be the singleplayer mode with one player and map where player cannot go out of bounds
		and the player has to follow the map

