3. implement multiplayer 

	phase 1: add a new package socket and create server and client
		create a new server class that creates a clienthandler for each clients
		create a new clent class that sends players location

	phase 3: client logic
		sends player location with pos in fornt of it
		/*		pos|x|y		*/

	Phase 3-4: create a clienthandler and its logic
		use static to add client in the lists
		it accepts clients and check message if its initail character is pos then its position
		send the player location to all the players in the list

	/*					completion

		this marks the completion of the actual phase 3.
