				multi player -> runs multiplayer mode
				inventory -> nohing
				exit -> exits game
				logout -> sends you to old or new player
	*/

	
4. implement jdbc in server

	phase 1: combine the socket and jdbc
		add jdbc code in socket package
		now the clienthandler will handle the jdbc connection and login and register
	
	phase 2-3: add login,register logic and add connecting in the pannel
		now the client will send playerid with login keyword and player name with name keyword
		/*   login|playerid		*/
		/*   name|playername		*/
		extract id or name form the clent message
		same logic that check the name with database and
		hanndle the wrong name,id and server error by send msg with distint keyword

